Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.93,0:00:17.09,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting lonelier and lonelier.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.55,0:00:19.98,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Does she really live in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.98,0:00:25.68,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,The lesser spirits said they saw someone who \Nlooked like Felt coming in this direction...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.01,0:00:31.50,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.50,0:00:33.71,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Does a girl named Felt live up this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.16,0:00:36.04,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Felt?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.02,0:00:39.43,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing that way but \NOld Man Rom's loot house.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.30,0:00:44.00,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Did Felt steal something from you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.58,0:00:47.15,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, go try and negotiate to get it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.15,0:00:48.66,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Live strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.55,0:00:59.39,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to pay money to get \Nback something stolen from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.81,0:01:02.66,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, at any rate, leave this one to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.09,0:01:04.77,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll negotiate with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.28,0:01:09.08,Default,Emiliar,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.08,0:01:10.79,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You agreed to that awfully easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.36,0:01:12.94,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The way you've been acting, \NI thought you'd say,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.94,0:01:15.00,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,"Leave this to a useless boy like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.00,0:01:17.43,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's so ridiculous, \NI'm laughing my head off!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.43,0:01:21.01,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And I'd be hurt, but still make up \Nmy mind to help you all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.01,0:01:23.48,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't say something that mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.48,0:01:27.64,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I'd be lying if I said \Nyou haven't been holding me back...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.64,0:01:29.25,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be a lie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.25,0:01:30.02,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.67,0:01:32.40,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try believing in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.17,0:01:36.94,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,If it actually goes well, \NI'll consider it a bonus.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.94,0:01:38.72,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd look up at me and say,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.72,0:01:42.20,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,"Do your best for me!" \NI'd feel a lot more motivated.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.75,0:01:44.62,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I can't force myself to \Nsay something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.58,0:01:47.91,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,But... do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.15,0:01:51.67,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.10,0:01:54.80,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go in first. You stay \Noutside and keep watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.80,0:01:58.00,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be back too late, \Nbut you can have dinner without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.00,0:01:59.68,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say dumb things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.68,0:02:00.69,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.69,0:02:01.68,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.31,0:02:05.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come in until I \Nsay it's okay, Satella.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.14,0:02:08.93,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.93,0:02:11.23,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing. Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.75,0:02:15.02,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,If you can get my insignia \Nback, I'll apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.13,0:02:20.36,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.24,0:02:29.51,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Now, am I walking into a \Ndemon nest or a snake pit?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.51,0:02:32.54,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,In a fantasy world, \Neither one is totally plausible...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.16,0:02:35.08,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,This is all stolen loot?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.08,0:02:37.47,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And why isn't there anyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.47,0:02:40.18,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,A place that handles stolen goods \Ncan only afford to be so careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.38,0:03:07.81,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear, you found that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.81,0:03:09.41,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I have no choice, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.80,0:03:11.84,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I have no choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.85,0:03:21.71,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, that burns...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.21,0:03:31.10,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap... Is all of this my blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.12,0:03:36.94,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad... Very bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.31,0:03:41.84,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.84,0:03:42.53,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:46.28,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No... Run! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:08.59,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait there...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:10.68,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.19,0:04:12.83,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:16.23,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,save you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.85,0:04:24.03,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, boy? \NYou look like you saw a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.76,0:04:26.49,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.29,0:04:29.74,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,I asked you about the appa. The appa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.74,0:04:31.45,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,Do you even have money?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:33.21,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:37.66,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,Don't "what" me! The appa! \NAre you buying it or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.66,0:04:41.49,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... No, like I said, \NI'm broke beyond compare...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.49,0:04:44.45,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,The hell? If you're just \Nbrowsing, then move along.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.45,0:04:47.68,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,I run a business here. I don't \Nhave time for window-shoppers
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.16,0:05:02.28,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.95,0:05:05.35,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it just nighttime a minute ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.01,0:05:09.24,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The wound on my belly is gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:13.61,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right! Satella!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.61,0:05:17.11,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, didn't Puck ask \Nme to take care of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.11,0:05:18.96,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get back to that shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:32.77,Default,Kan,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why do you look so spooked?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:35.83,Default,Chin,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't wanna get hurt, \Ncough up whatever you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:38.90,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You guys... Did you see I was \Nalone and decide to get revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.24,0:05:41.37,Default,Chin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.37,0:05:43.13,Default,Kan,0000,0000,0000,,Are you nuts?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.13,0:05:44.56,Default,Ton,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.56,0:05:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave everything you've got \Non the ground and we'll let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.23,0:05:50.90,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, fine. Everything I've got, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.90,0:05:52.88,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in a hurry, so I don't even care.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.88,0:05:54.43,Default,Kan,0000,0000,0000,,Now act like a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.43,0:05:57.67,Default,Kan,0000,0000,0000,,Get on all fours like a \Ndog and howl, "Help me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:06:00.67,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get cocky, bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.08,0:06:10.20,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.91,0:06:16.10,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate a truant \Nkid with too much free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:19.83,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,After swinging a wooden sword around \Nall the time for no reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.83,0:06:22.68,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,my grip strength is over 70 kilograms!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.08,0:06:31.51,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in a hurry! Don't get in my way again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.82,0:06:37.50,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't freak out... \NDon't freak out, don't freak out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.48,0:06:47.00,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Am I stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.00,0:06:49.76,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,After coming this far, I can't \Njust leave without answers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:53.99,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Is anyone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:57.00,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Someone... Someone's in there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.00,0:06:59.23,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Please, answer me! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:01.06,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,Shut yer trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:03.62,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,You tryin' to bust my \Ndoor down when you don't
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.62,0:07:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even know the signal or password?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:12.24,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.52,0:07:21.58,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,What're you all fidgety for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:23.92,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,Are your balls chafin' ya that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:26.42,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not worried about the \Nposition of my privates!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:28.36,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't start the conversation \Nwith potty humor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.36,0:07:31.09,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,You're already interrupting \Nmy evening booze.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.36,0:07:35.78,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,You'll kill me if you start \Ntalkin' about boring stuff now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.78,0:07:39.14,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't drink while the sun's \Nstill up. You'll die young.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:42.37,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, this is a dumb question, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.61,0:07:46.15,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Have you died recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.51,0:07:54.66,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I admit I'm an old \Nman at death's door,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:56.83,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,but I ain't really died yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.17,0:07:59.54,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then have you seen \Na girl with silver hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,0:08:01.09,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,Silver hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.43,0:08:04.29,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't seen anyone that conspicuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.44,0:08:08.36,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Was it all a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.82,0:08:11.12,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Then exactly how much of it was a dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.12,0:08:13.51,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,and why am I in this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.78,0:08:17.01,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,So what are you doin' here, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:19.86,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I'm looking for an insignia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.86,0:08:22.75,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It belongs to a silver-haired \Ngirl who helped me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.75,0:08:25.52,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why, but it's important to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:28.98,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I think she said it had \Na jewel in the center.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.35,0:08:31.66,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,An insignia with a jewel...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.23,0:08:34.95,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I ain't got anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:37.79,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure? Try to think!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:39.52,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you're just old and senile?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.52,0:08:41.98,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't remember when I'm \Nat my best, with booze in me,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.98,0:08:44.56,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,the only explanation is \Nthat I don't know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.02,0:08:46.21,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:49.64,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,I've got someone bringing \Nin some goods later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.64,0:08:52.17,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm told it's some fine loot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.17,0:08:56.22,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,There's a good chance it could \Nbe what you're lookin' for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:58.18,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Is the one bringing it in a girl named Felt?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.41,0:09:01.70,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,What, you even know who swiped it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.70,0:09:06.92,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, whether you'll be able \Nto afford it is another matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.92,0:09:09.78,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! It's no use trying to size me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.78,0:09:12.60,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm as broke as they come, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.60,0:09:14.68,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't no use talkin' about it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.68,0:09:18.20,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No, there is the option of trading.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:23.02,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, \Nyou've got some unusual stuff there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:26.73,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. For example, \Nthis is a corn potage snack.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.73,0:09:28.07,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's super tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.07,0:09:29.88,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,That's food?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.27,0:09:39.89,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,I see! What an odd flavor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:42.02,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,These would go great with booze!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.02,0:09:43.49,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Right? Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.49,0:09:45.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't just start eating them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:48.18,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I dunno what you plan to trade,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.18,0:09:51.04,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,but you'll have to come \Nback after Felt gets here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.04,0:09:53.61,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,Mm, that's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:09.54,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I guess in any world, there are people \Nwith money, and people without.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:12.80,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is easy to see the difference here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.64,0:10:21.60,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what're you doing there? \NYou're in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.29,0:10:24.25,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Felt!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.25,0:10:26.10,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,You know me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:28.31,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I do! I've been waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.88,0:10:30.23,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.78,0:10:34.29,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, are you saying you don't remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:36.33,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Have we met?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.33,0:10:39.10,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I'm a busy woman, \Nso I don't remember most people
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.10,0:10:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I meet unless they leave a huge impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.38,0:10:43.93,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say that was a pretty huge impression...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.93,0:10:45.45,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.45,0:10:47.87,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I want to negotiate for \Nthe insignia you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.73,0:10:52.65,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that's it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.65,0:10:54.23,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll hear you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:10:57.12,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,For a rat...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.12,0:10:57.77,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.77,0:10:59.12,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,For a white whale...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:10:59.12,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,A harpoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.12,0:11:00.80,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,To the noble dragon lord, we are...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:01.81,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Shitbags.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.48,0:11:05.43,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting, Old Man Rom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:07.09,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,My target was more persistent \Nthan I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.09,0:11:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It took a while to shake them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.24,0:11:17.32,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Old Man Rom, did you \Nwater down this milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.32,0:11:18.30,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,It's nasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.30,0:11:22.24,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I give you something outta the goodness \Nof my heart, and you call it gross?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.65,0:11:25.62,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You two are closer than I had \Neither hoped or expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:27.57,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm feeling left out over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.57,0:11:31.33,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk like a wuss when you've got a \Nface almost as scary as Old Man Rom's.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.80,0:11:33.89,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,People have said many things to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.89,0:11:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you tell me I can \Ncompete with this old guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:39.21,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I went too far that time. Sorry, Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.58,0:11:43.93,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,You two aren't in some conspiracy \Nto try to piss me off, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:47.90,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, well, why don't we \Nget down to business?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.90,0:11:49.59,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,How much will you pay for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.59,0:11:51.18,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You don't waste time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.18,0:11:53.69,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Before I answer that, you do \Nhave the insignia, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:55.25,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.24,0:11:57.29,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.29,0:12:04.51,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,This one's got a jewel in it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.51,0:12:07.02,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,so I had to work pretty hard to get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.02,0:12:10.14,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,If you can pay enough to match \Nmy effort, we'll both be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.14,0:12:11.36,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I have no money.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.09,0:12:14.49,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Then we have nothing to discuss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.49,0:12:19.46,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk, tsk, tsk. I don't have money, \Nbut I have things worth money.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:23.35,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What I have here is a
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.35,0:12:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,magical device that can stop \Ntime for everyone, everywhere:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.23,0:12:27.90,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,a "cell phone"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:29.07,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.07,0:12:30.81,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,Never seen one of those before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.08,0:12:35.10,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! Nine shots per \Nsecond: Continuous Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:38.89,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Hey! What's that sound?! \NAnd that was too bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.89,0:12:41.12,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,Are you tryin' to kill me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.12,0:12:43.85,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you go makin' light of this old \Nman with dodgy tricks like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.85,0:12:45.11,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Now, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:46.49,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.29,0:12:49.65,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,Them's me and Felt's faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.65,0:12:51.30,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,What sort of magic is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.30,0:12:55.50,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, it's a mystical item \Nthat can freeze a moment in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.16,0:13:00.82,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,With this, you can capture moments \Nin time and store them in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.82,0:13:02.91,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,I see! That is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.91,0:13:04.42,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,Never seen the like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.42,0:13:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that one of the "metia" I've \Nbeen hearing about lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.98,0:13:07.72,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,"Metia"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:11.36,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,It's the name for devices \Nthat lets people who haven't
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.36,0:13:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,opened the gate use magic, \Nlike real magic users.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.22,0:13:17.03,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,I'm more concerned with the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.03,0:13:19.32,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,What can I get out of this metia?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.70,0:13:23.62,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's my first time using a metia, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.62,0:13:27.32,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,But I'd say there's no doubt it'll \Nfetch more than that insignia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:30.73,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Then that settles it! \NThis cell phone for the insignia!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.73,0:13:32.31,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Negotiations complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.73,0:13:33.54,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.28,0:13:35.62,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:36.63,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.63,0:13:39.42,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,You're not the only one I'm \Nnegotiating with for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.42,0:13:40.41,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.41,0:13:44.71,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I nabbed this insignia \Nbecause I was asked to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.71,0:13:48.03,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,My client told me I could \Nget ten holy coins for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.03,0:13:50.17,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You already had a deal with \Nthe one you stole it for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.17,0:13:53.14,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what ten holy \Ncoins would be worth, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.14,0:13:57.81,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,That metia you've got would be worth \Nat least twenty holy coins...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.81,0:14:01.53,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,No, there are probably fanciers out there \Nwho'd pay more for a thing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.53,0:14:04.90,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! That means I can get \Naway with overcharging for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:07.73,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So, when and where are \Nyou meeting your client?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.73,0:14:10.45,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. Negotiations will be held here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:12.96,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,If a little thing like \Nme dealt with them alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.96,0:14:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be sunk if a client \Ndecided to bilk on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.98,0:14:17.61,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't have to worry \Nwith Old Man Rom here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:22.58,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,Do they know the password?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.58,0:14:24.17,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I didn't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:26.50,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,That's probably for me. I'll go check.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.61,0:14:32.26,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You're okay with letting \Nher use you like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:34.57,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it ain't like we're total strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.57,0:14:38.37,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,I've known her a long time, \Nso I'll help her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:43.01,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You know, even I have to give \Na wry chuckle at the sight
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of someone looking like such a barbarian.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.39,0:14:46.99,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,Well, look at where we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:49.98,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone around here is \Ndesperate just to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.98,0:14:52.82,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,It's common for youngsters \Nto join forces with others
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.82,0:14:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in similar situations to \Nkeep themselves alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.59,0:14:57.38,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,But Felt ain't cut out for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.38,0:15:00.45,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I gotta look out for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.30,0:15:04.66,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,I was right. It was for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.35,0:15:07.11,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Over here. Care to sit down?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.11,0:15:09.57,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,There seem to be several outsiders here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:11.81,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'd be in trouble if you bilked on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.81,0:15:13.68,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,We weaklings have our own brand of smarts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.07,0:15:17.93,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,I know this older fellow, \Nbut who's the young man?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:19.69,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's your rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:22.99,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,He's the other person negotiating with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:34.37,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.90,0:15:36.52,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,I understand the situation now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.52,0:15:40.33,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,So that means you two will be \Nbidding against each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.33,0:15:43.61,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really care who gets the insignia,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.61,0:15:46.07,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll sell it to the highest bidder.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.07,0:15:48.42,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,I think I like that personality of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:51.35,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,So how much did this young man bid?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.35,0:15:53.78,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm putting up this metia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.78,0:15:56.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's a rare item, probably the only \None of its kind in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:16:01.60,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That muscleman tells me it's worth \Nno less than twenty holy coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.35,0:16:04.54,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,A metia...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.87,0:16:11.45,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,As it happens, the client sent \Nme with some extra funds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:13.70,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,Just so I'd be prepared to sweeten the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:17.68,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The client... So you were \Nasked to fetch it, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.68,0:16:21.01,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. The client \Nis the one who wants it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.01,0:16:22.82,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,Would you happen to be in the same business?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.82,0:16:25.57,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Being in the same business as me \Nwould mean they're unemployed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.13,0:16:31.07,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,So, this unemployed guy has named a \Nprice that puts him far in the lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:34.09,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,What price is your master putting on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.82,0:16:48.52,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.76,0:16:52.42,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,These are all the holy coins \Nmy employer sent with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.89,0:16:54.46,Default,Else,0000,0000,0000,,Is it not quite enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.55,0:16:58.53,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,You're a man! Don't make that pathetic face!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:17:03.00,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, your metia is \Nworth no less than twenty...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.78,0:17:07.63,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,As I see it, victory in this \Ndeal is leaning toward the boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:12.67,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for you and your employer, but you'd \Nbetter bag up those coins and leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.36,0:17:18.28,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:24.67,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What? What's wrong with a little \Nvictory pose? I'm psyched!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.67,0:17:26.41,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,No one said anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.41,0:17:29.96,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Go as crazy as you want. I don't \Ncare, as long as I get my profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:34.44,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, sorry, Elsa-san. \NYou'll probably get in trouble, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.94,0:17:36.76,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.76,0:17:40.95,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,It was my employer's fault \Nfor trying to underpay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:47.34,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this deal ended in \Ndisappointment for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.34,0:17:49.33,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,but I'll be taking my leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.61,0:17:55.56,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what do you intend \Nto do with that insignia?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.56,0:17:58.51,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm going to find its \Nowner and return it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:09.32,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... You're with them, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.32,0:18:13.26,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.26,0:18:14.79,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.79,0:18:17.54,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my. You dodged my strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.15,0:18:29.67,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,This is my first battle to \Nthe death with a giant!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:33.68,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet, little girl! I'll grind \Nyou up and feed you to the rats!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.82,0:18:48.65,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.65,0:18:50.90,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. There's no way \NOld Man Rom will lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:53.52,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.42,0:18:59.86,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Old Man Rom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:04.17,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.77,0:19:05.92,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.92,0:19:07.70,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,I can at least take you with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.77,0:19:13.97,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:24.06,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll return this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.86,0:19:30.84,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,You bitch... How dare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.84,0:19:33.63,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? It seems you have more \Ncourage than your friend there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.14,0:19:37.28,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,But if you resist, \Nyou might very well get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.76,0:19:42.36,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you, even if you don't \Nfight back, you psychopath!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.70,0:19:45.51,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,If you move around, my hands might slip.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.51,0:19:47.87,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm quite rough at handling blades, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.47,0:19:50.79,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry you got caught up in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:51.92,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:54.23,Default - italics,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,Blessing of the Wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:19:59.31,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,How wonderful. I can see you \Nare loved by this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.31,0:20:01.19,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,I envy you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.79,0:20:17.81,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,The old man and the girl have \Nfallen, yet you aren't moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.81,0:20:19.44,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,Have you given up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.87,0:20:22.38,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,D-Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.74,0:20:26.86,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you finally stood up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.86,0:20:30.45,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,It's less fun since you took \Nso long, but still, not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.35,0:20:45.24,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use, though. I can see you're a \Nnovice, and your movements are rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:46.98,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,You have no blessings or techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.98,0:20:49.68,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,I'd hoped I could squeeze wisdom out \Nof you, but you lack that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:53.02,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I do have my pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:55.77,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,After you put me through all this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.47,0:20:59.18,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,I do acknowledge that you have \Nextraordinary determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.18,0:21:01.11,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,If only you could've done that sooner,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:03.95,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,things might have gone \Ndifferently for these two.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.63,0:21:16.63,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's time to end this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.63,0:21:18.55,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send you to meet the angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.16,0:21:40.03,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... I certainly felt that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.96,0:21:49.04,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,Are you surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.56,0:21:52.60,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,I opened up your belly when \Nwe passed by one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.60,0:21:55.38,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,This is the one thing I excel at.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.26,0:22:02.05,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.50,0:22:06.55,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,Your guts have such a lovely color!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.94,0:22:09.60,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts... It hurts... \NIt hurts... It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.60,0:22:11.16,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts... It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.16,0:22:12.96,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,Does it hurt? Are you suffering?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.16,0:22:13.86,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It... doesn't hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.96,0:22:15.32,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,In pain? Sad? Do you want to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.32,0:22:16.48,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Die?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.48,0:22:20.72,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Am I dead? Am I still alive? \NWhen will I die? When will I die?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.72,0:22:27.80,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,Slowly, slowly, slowly, slowly...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.84,0:22:24.23,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared... I'm scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.23,0:22:27.70,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared! I'm scared! I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.70,0:22:29.70,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna die! I'm gonna \Ndie! I'm gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.70,0:22:32.11,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you're slowly losing body heat...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.82,0:22:36.75,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,You're slowly growing cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.75,0:22:39.01,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I'm dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.12,0:22:45.30,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, boy? \NYou look like you saw a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.88,0:22:47.93,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,Boy? You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.41,0:22:52.04,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what's going on anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.71,0:23:01.59,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.59,0:23:04.57,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,Here, forget about the money. \NJust take these.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.13,0:23:15.62,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.18,0:23:19.12,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Please, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.62,0:23:22.80,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Satella!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.15,0:23:26.64,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't ignore me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.64,0:23:30.04,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,My dying and not doing what \Nyou said were my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.54,0:23:32.73,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But I was desperate!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.30,0:23:37.18,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I went back to the loot house after \Nthat, but I couldn't find you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.77,0:23:42.80,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for only thinking of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.15,0:23:45.98,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad you're all right, Satella.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.08,0:23:50.15,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.94,0:23:53.73,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.73,0:23:56.20,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,but don't call me by the \Nname of the Jealous Witch!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.20,0:23:57.56,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking?!
